{"title":"Dismovilismo","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría/Orto Dismovilismo-2026.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"# 25. DISMOVILISMO\\N(Síndrome de Inmovilidad)","guid":"qlCVWaZvvEO3mDujRY-rYw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Dismovilismo","guid":"f1VNEpYVjUCNNSoo6dIy1Q","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definición y Conceptos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"**Disminución de la capacidad para\\Ndesempeñar AVD** por deterioro de\\Nfunciones motoras","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Síndrome geriátrico →\\Nmulticomponente, multicausal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Espectro: movilidad reducida →\\N**encamamiento total**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"Discordancia entre recuperación\\Nmédica y funcional → \"alta\\Nmédica ≠ alta funcional\"","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"Relacionado con **Deterioro Funcional\\NAsociado a Hospitalización (DAH)**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"Definición DAH → pérdida de ≥1\\NAVD tras hospitalización","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Prevalencia global ~**30%** adultos\\Nmayores hospitalizados (Loyd C, 2020)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Chile (DEIS 2019)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"**23.2%** egresos hospitalarios\\N→ personas >64 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Estancia hospitalaria promedio → 8.3 días\\N(<80a) vs **9.3 días** (≥80a)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"Aumento progresivo desde 2001 (**16.\\N5%**) hasta 2019 (**23.2%**)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Impacto pronóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Nueva discapacidad en ABVD al alta →\\Nmortalidad 1 año **41%** vs 17% sin\\Ndiscapacidad (Boyd, 2008)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Recuperación funcional al mes post-alta →\\Nreduce mortalidad a la mitad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"<**50%** recuperan\\Nfuncionalidad pre-enfermedad al\\Naño","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"10","text":"Principal preocupación del adulto mayor →\\N**\"depender de otros\"** (6ta Encuesta\\NUC-Caja Los Andes, 2022)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"1","text":"Factores de Riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Pre-hospitalización\\N(vulnerabilidad basal)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Edad avanzada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"**Fragilidad** (CFS ≥5)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Deterioro cognitivo previo / Demencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Dependencia previa en ABVD o AIVD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"21","text":"Depresión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"21","text":"Funcionamiento social deficiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"21","text":"Baja movilidad previa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"20","text":"Durante hospitalización\\N(peligros del entorno)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Entorno no familiar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"**Reposo en cama prolongado**\\N→ causa más relevante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"29","text":"Restricciones físicas\\N(barandas, contenciones)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"29","text":"Catéteres y dispositivos invasivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"29","text":"Polifarmacia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"29","text":"Procedimientos invasivos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"29","text":"Malnutrición","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"29","text":"Deprivación sensorial","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"20","text":"Post-hospitalización","guid":"","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Entorno domiciliario inadecuado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"Falta de recursos de rehabilitación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"Apoyo\\Ncomunitario/familiar\\Ninsuficiente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"1","text":"Fisiopatología → \"Cascada hacia la\\NDependencia\" (Creditor, 1993)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Sistema musculoesquelético","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Pérdida de fuerza muscular →\\N**5% por día** de reposo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Acortamiento\\Nmuscular y\\Ncontracturas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"**Sarcopenia aguda** → 28\\Ndías de hospitalización","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Mecanismos → desuso +\\Ninflamación aguda + ↑cortisol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Potenciadores → delirium,\\Nmalnutrición, inmovilidad, corticoides","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"43","text":"Desmineralización ósea →\\N**50x** tasa normal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Pérdida de 10 días → requiere **4\\Nmeses** para recuperar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"43","text":"Reacondicionamiento → toma el **doble de\\Ntiempo** que desacondicionamiento","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"42","text":"Sistema cardiovascular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Pérdida **600 cc**\\Nvolumen plasmático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Pérdida sensibilidad barorreceptores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"**Hipotensión ortostática** y síncope","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"↑ Riesgo trombosis venosa profunda","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Población de alto riesgo → fracturas\\Nextremidad inferior (Jian Y, 2026)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"42","text":"Sistema respiratorio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"↓ Ventilación pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"PaO2 puede ↓ hasta **8 mmHg**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"Riesgo de insuficiencia respiratoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"Atelectasias y\\Nneumonía por\\Naspiración","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"42","text":"Sistema genitourinario","guid":"","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"Prevalencia incontinencia → 5-15%\\Nambulatorio vs **40-50%** hospitalizado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"Infecciones urinarias por catéteres","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"Retención urinaria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"42","text":"Piel","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Presión >32 mmHg por >2h\\N→ necrosis tisular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Presión sacro ~70 mmHg,\\Ntalones ~45 mmHg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"**Úlceras por presión** → alto riesgo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"42","text":"Sistema neurológico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Deprivación sensorial → confusión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"Hiperestimulación → **Delirium**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"Deterioro cognitivo acelerado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"71","text":"Depresión reactiva","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"42","text":"Estado nutricional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"\"Tormenta perfecta\" → pérdida\\Ngusto/olfato + menor sed + anorexia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"**Desnutrición y\\Ndeshidratación**\\Nintrahospitalaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"Disfagia sarcopénica → 4.3% desarrollan\\Ntrastornos deglución (Maeda K, 2019)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"1","text":"Consecuencias Clínicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Funcionales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"Pérdida de ABVD y AIVD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Incapacidad para\\Nmarcha independiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"Dependencia para transferencias","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"80","text":"Complicaciones médicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Tromboembolismo\\Nvenoso (TVP/TEP)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"Úlceras por presión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"Infecciones nosocomiales (ITU, NAV)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"Estreñimiento → fecalomas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"Neumonía aspirativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"Caídas al intentar movilización","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"80","text":"Outcomes adversos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"↑ Mortalidad intrahospitalaria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"↑ Institucionalización","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"↑ Readmisiones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"92","text":"↑ Costos sanitarios","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"1","text":"Evaluación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Valoración funcional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"**Índice de Barthel** → basal\\Nvs actual (Δ Barthel)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"Lawton-Brody (AIVD)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"Functional\\NIndependence Measure\\N(FIM)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"Valoración de movilidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"**Timed Up and Go** (TUG) → >20\\Nseg = alto riesgo caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"Velocidad de marcha →\\N<0.8 m/s patológico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"102","text":"SPPB (Short Physical\\NPerformance Battery)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"102","text":"Escala de movilidad de cama","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"97","text":"Evaluación de fragilidad","guid":"","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"**Clinical Frailty Scale** (CFS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"FRAIL Scale","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"Fried Phenotype","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"97","text":"Evaluación nutricional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"MNA (Mini Nutritional Assessment)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"Circunferencia de\\Npantorrilla → sarcopenia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"111","text":"Albúmina, prealbúmina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"97","text":"Evaluación cognitiva","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"CAM/CAM-ICU → delirium","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"MMSE/MoCA → deterioro cognitivo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"97","text":"Evaluación de riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Walter Prognostic Index\\N→ mortalidad 1 año","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Sexo masculino → 1 pto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"Dependencia 1-4 AIVD → 1 pto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"Dependencia 5-6 AIVD → 2 ptos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"119","text":"Dependencia ≥1 ABVD → 2 ptos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"ICC → 1 pto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"119","text":"Cáncer (no piel) → 2 ptos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"119","text":"EPOC → 1 pto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"119","text":"DM → 1 pto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"119","text":"Albúmina <3.4 g/dL → 1 pto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"119","text":"Creatinina >3.0 mg/dL → 1 pto","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"118","text":"Dependencia total ABVD → mortalidad 1\\Naño **34%** (> cáncer aislado)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"1","text":"Prevención e Intervención","guid":"","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Principio fundamental","guid":"","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"**>50% del DAH es\\Niatrogénico y prevenible**","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"132","text":"**2/3 a 80%** de causas →\\Npotencialmente reversibles","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"Causas reversibles principales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"1. **Reposo prolongado en\\Ncama** (la más relevante)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"2. Falta de estímulo a continencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"3. Valoración nutricional inadecuada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"135","text":"4. Reacción adversa a fármacos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"131","text":"Intervenciones basadas en sistema","guid":"","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"**Unidades Geriátricas\\NAgudas (UGA/ACE Units)**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"NNT=**19** → prevenir\\Ndeterioro funcional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"NNT=**17** → evitar\\Ninstitucionalización","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"Equipo multidisciplinario +\\Nadaptaciones ambientales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"140","text":"**Hospital Elder Life\\NProgram (HELP)**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Orientación + nutrición + movilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"↓ Incidencia delirium y caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"Implementable por\\Nfamiliares (estudio chileno)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"140","text":"Rehabilitación\\Ngeriátrica\\Nintrahospitalaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Ejercicios de resistencia\\N→ mejoran SPPB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"↓ Deterioro funcional,\\Ninstitucionalización y mortalidad","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"131","text":"Medidas específicas\\N(\"Geriatrizar\" la atención)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"VGI inicial → identificar\\Npacientes de riesgo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"**Movilización precoz** →\\Nfundamental para prevención TVP","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"Evitar restricciones a movilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Remover dispositivos\\Ninvasivos precozmente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Fomentar ABVD independiente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"152","text":"Modificaciones ambientales (camas\\Nbajas, evitar barandas altas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"152","text":"Revisión diaria de fármacos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"152","text":"Optimización nutricional → evitar\\Ndietas restrictivas innecesarias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"152","text":"Planificación del alta desde el ingreso","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"131","text":"Interconsulta geriatría","guid":"","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"Aislada → **NO** ha\\Nmostrado beneficios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"Éxito → **trabajo en equipo\\Nmultidisciplinario**","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"1","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"[**5% de fuerza muscular se pierde por\\Ndía** de reposo en cama → recuperar\\Ntoma el doble de tiempo]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"[Nueva dependencia en 1 ABVD durante\\Nhospitalización → **duplica mortalidad a\\N1 año** (17% → 41%)]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"[Recuperar funcionalidad en\\N**primer mes** post-alta →\\Nreduce mortalidad a la mitad]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"[**>50%** del deterioro funcional\\Nhospitalario es iatrogénico y prevenible]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"165","text":"[Reposo prolongado es la **causa\\Nreversible más importante** →\\Nmovilización precoz es mandatoria]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"165","text":"[40-50% de AM hospitalizados\\Ndesarrollan incontinencia → muchos\\Nno eran incontinentes previo]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"165","text":"[UGA tiene NNT=19 para prevenir\\Ndeterioro y NNT=17 para evitar\\Ninstitucionalización]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"165","text":"[Interconsulta geriátrica aislada es\\Nineficaz → el beneficio está en el\\N**equipo multidisciplinario**]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"165","text":"[Dependencia total en ABVD →\\Nmortalidad 34% a 1 año (supera\\Na cáncer aislado)]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"165","text":"[Sarcopenia aguda se desarrolla en 28 días →\\Ninflamación + desuso + cortisol]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"165","text":"[Movilización temprana en fractura\\Ncadera → esencial para prevenir TVP\\Ny mejorar outcomes]","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"165","text":"[Menos del 50% de AM recuperan\\Nfuncionalidad pre-enfermedad al año del alta]","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"2z9296rx-UKLBOaV9wmsng","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"1. Creditor MC. Hazards of\\Nhospitalization of the elderly. Ann\\NIntern Med. 1993;118(3):219-23.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"2. Boyd CM, et al. Recovery of activities of daily\\Nliving in older adults after hospitalization. J Am\\NGeriatr Soc. 2008;56(12):2171-9.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"3. Loyd C, et al. Prevalence of hospital-associated\\Ndisability in older adults: A meta-analysis. J Am Med\\NDir Assoc. 2020;21(4):455-461.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"4. Maeda K, et al. Development and Predictors of Sarcopenic\\NDysphagia during Hospitalization of Older Adults. Nutrients.\\N2019;12(1):70. DOI: 10.3390/nu12010070","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"178","text":"5. Jian Y, et al. Perioperative Deep Vein Thrombosis in\\NElderly Patients with Lower Extremity Fracture. Clin Appl\\NThromb Hemost. 2026;32:10760296261417219. DOI: 10.\\N1177/10760296261417219","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"178","text":"6. Gallardo N. Deterioro Funcional en\\NPersonas Mayores Hospitalizadas.\\N[Presentación]. Chile.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"178","text":"7. Walter LC, et al. Development and validation\\Nof a prognostic index for 1-year mortality.\\NJAMA. 2001;285(23):2987-94.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"178","text":"8. Landefeld CS, et al. A randomized trial of care\\Nin a hospital medical unit especially designed to\\Nimprove functional outcomes. N Engl J Med.\\N1995;332(20):1338-44.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":187,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Ortogeriatría","filename":"Orto Dismovilismo-2026","id":"map_1528","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Orto Dismovilismo-2026"}